descriptions.early_strength: Short-term trend of RS is upward (RS slope > 0)
descriptions.medium_strength: RS slope is up and RS is above its 13-day average
descriptions.strong_strength: RS slope is up, RS is above RS13, and RS13 is above RS49 (long-term uptrend)
descriptions.early_weakness: Short-term trend of RS is downward (RS slope  0)
descriptions.medium_weakness: RS slope is down and RS is below its 13-day average
descriptions.strong_weakness: RS slope is down, RS is below RS13, and RS13 is below RS49 (long-term downtrend)
